{"id":"summaries/2021-11-21-collective-hallucination","title":"Collective hallucination","type":"summaries","html":"<p>Title-only concept-stub from November 2021 by <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/yahir-gonzalez\">Yahir</a> — <em>\"Collective hallucination\"</em> (the framing of money / markets / nation-states as agreed-upon fictions). Sits adjacent to the <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/crypto\">crypto</a> / <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/disruption\">disruption</a> cluster as a foundational thinking primitive.</p>\n<p><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/yahir-gonzalez\">yahir gonzalez</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/crypto\">crypto</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/disruption\">disruption</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/nonobvious\">nonobvious</a></p>\n","related":[{"id":"concepts/crypto","label":"Crypto"},{"id":"concepts/disruption","label":"Disruption"},{"id":"concepts/nonobvious","label":"Nonobvious"},{"id":"entities/yahir-gonzalez","label":"Yahir Gonzalez"}]}
